---
title: Beef & Pork Pasta Bacon Bolognese with Cherry Tomatoes & Pear Salad
description: Packed with the rich flavours of a classic Italian tomato sauce, you'll find it hard to believe this beef bolognese didn't involve hours
of cooking. Plus, with veggies hidden in the sauce, it creates a beautifully textured and mouth-watering meal everyone will love.

*We’ve replaced the penne in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
